title: DNSK - The Ghettoblaster (Rock Steady)
description:
I made this mix late in the night after reviewing "Ghetto Funk Mix June 2014" from last summer that has poor audio quality on some of the tracks used. This one has good sound though on all of its 24 carefully selected and uttermost delicious ghetto funk tunes that are derived from the Interwebz.

Enjoy and thank you for listening!

TRACKLIST:

01. The Captain - H2H (DNSK Re-Cut)
02. Jackson 5 - ABC (A.Skillz Remix)
03. Stickybuds - Been Real, Murderer, Don't Deny It, Out Of Debt
04. Parker - Hear Ya Say
05. Beatles - Come Together (A.Skillz Remix, FK5 Video Edit)
06. Aretha Franklin - Rock Steady (Parker Remix)
07. Kidda - Wanna Be Loved (Dancefloor Outlaws Remix, DNSK Re-Cut)
08. J-Roc (Sould Out DJs) - Nickelodeon (DNSK Re-Cut)
09. Ray Charles - Good Thymes (Opiuo Remix)
10. The Asteroids Galaxy Tour - Golden Age (Pimpsoul's Refunk)
11. Pimpsoul - On Point
12. Eric Clapton - Cocaine (Dancefloor Outlaws Remix, DNSK Intro Re-Cut)
13. The Sly Players - On The Hook (The Captain Remix)
14. Mooqee & Pimpsoul - Keep Pounding (Original Mix)
15. Fdel - Rocksteady (DNSK Remix)
16. Mooqee & Pimpsoul - Do It
17. Toastbusters - Dope 'n' Spicey
18. Chase & Status feat. Kano - Against All Odds
19. The Dancefloor Outlaws - Betty Beat
20. Fort Knox Five - Papa was Stoned
21. The Breakbeat Junkie vs. DJP - Drop Down (DNSK Re-Cut)
22. Bob Marley - Jammin' (CMC & Silenta Remix)
23. DJ Deekline & Ed Solo feat. Booty Pit - Wu Tang Sausage
24. Defunk - Banjo Blues (Original Mix)
